expressionObjects: logicalColumn:SSYS_SF.Dim - Supplier Site.Supplier Site Buyer Id

logicalColumns.name: Site Status
logicalColumns.description:
According to INACTIVE_DATE field:
CASE WHEN TimeStampDiff (SQL_TSI_DAY,"SSYS"."Dim - Supplier Site"."Inactive Date" , current_date) >= 0 THEN 'InActive' ELSE 'Current' END

logicalExpression.expressionTemplate: CASE  WHEN  TIMESTAMPDIFF( SQL_TSI_DAY , %1,  CURRENT_DATE ) >= 0 THEN 'InActive' ELSE 'Current' END
CASE  WHEN %1 <=  CURRENT_DATE  AND  CURRENT_DATE  <=  IFNULL(%2,  CURRENT_DATE  + 1) THEN 'Y' ELSE 'N' END

logicalColumns.name: Supplier Site Buyer BI User Name

logicalExpression.expressionTemplate: CASE  WHEN %1 = %2 THEN 'Y' WHEN %1 IS NULL  THEN 'Y' WHEN %1 <> %2 THEN 'N' END
